Code Meaning 0 Success 1 User or validation error (bad input, missing config, schema drift) 2 Internal or unexpected error 130 Interrupted (Ctrl+C) <p>In <code>--json</code> mode, errors include an <code>error_type</code> field for automation:</p> <pre><code>{
  "ok": false,
  "command": "model publish",
  "data": {
    "error": "No completed versions found in lock file. Specify --version explicitly.",
    "error_type": "runtime_error"
  }
}
</code></pre>
